      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "At the next meeting of the Cen\ntrail Labor union. Monday night,\nThomas Maloney of the legislative\ncommittee will ask that man be\nelected by the union on salary to\ntake care Of the petitions to which\nnames of voters will be signed as\na means of securing the initiative,\nreferendum and recall amendment\nto the city charter.\n\n\nThis is no small job, and Mr..\nNaloney stated this morning that\nne would be unable to take care\nof the petitions and do his other\nwork. Afildavits must be secured\nfrom every one of the voters sign\ning the petition that 1t may be\nshown conclusively that the sig\nnatures on the paper are genuine,"
    }
  ]
